{"tid":1812262,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「抗鳩拉運動」遊行路線如果係旺區，政府鳩拉就等如幫手加速經濟攬炒","createTime":"2020-01-05T10:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T16:33:36.000Z","uid":52023,"like":80,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"7edda72aff04e6ced09dc3c99bec2bbb33572610","tid":1812262,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:55:30.000Z","msg":"遊行路線如果喺旺區<br />\n政府鳩拉就等如幫手加速經濟攬炒<br />\n相信有行過尖咀海運嗰頭都知星期日已經少人過閪咁<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>政府出到鳩拉絕對係七傷拳<br />\n依家要做嘅係加大政府鳩拉成本<br />\n</strong></span>以力打力 傷人自傷<br />\n<br />\n上季度零售數據已經再跌兩成<br />\n唔好諗住零售還零售 對其它行業冇影響<br />\n零售收皮最後條數又係回歸地產商<br />\n依家政府想玩批不反再鳩拉絕對唔會係冇成本<br />\n仲會成為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>令到經濟攬炒加速</strong></span></span>嘅原兇<br />\n<br />\n黑警出到七傷拳對付運動<br />\n即係同出面某個POST所講嘅一樣<br />\n政府覺得已經冇條件再磨落去<br />\n需要盡快解決<br />\n而根據時間表最合理嘅推測就係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">政府希望喺農歷年之前<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">遏止所有遊行示威活動嘅參與者</span><br />\n再喺接近農歷新年嘅時候唔批不反<br />\n造成回復社會平靜嘅假像<br />\n俾商界喺農歷新年回血 <br />\n從而淡化黃色經濟圈對支資嘅影響<br />\n再靠農歷新年嘅消費數據去證明社會運作暢順<br />\n令示威者覺得所有行動都不可行<br />\n而令運動完結</span></span></strong><br />\n呢個亦係我覺得點解最近官媒同狗官出盡奶力都要唱衰黃圈嘅一大原因<br />\n就係為咗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">淡化黃圈對支資所造成嘅影響</span></strong></span>個形像<br />\n<br />\n除咗喺旺區遊行一定仲有更多方法<br />\n希望大家集思廣益出多幾招<br />\n既然依家係處於政府急我哋唔急嘅情況<br />\n理論上係更加可以有空間去思考吓點令呢場運動更有效"},{"pid":"5b680a0fd66767ed6aa5409adb3015fa964c625c","tid":1812262,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2276cb324f8824c2cc31976f6c350a0be00a5ef8","tid":1812262,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:58:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"757f98ec74c74bf6898f3732e4e2fc50099f7192","tid":1812262,"uid":33303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:59:29.000Z","msg":"第一次旺角 第二次銅鑼灣 叫唔叫旺區"},{"pid":"7712ceaf487c8a68cb7c53717aaab3a737461d33","tid":1812262,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:59:54.000Z","msg":"攬炒！"},{"pid":"738f9af8a7d999d6cefe8ccad8c22d9b61249b12","tid":1812262,"uid":34779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:01:42.000Z","msg":"香港政府都玩加速主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c458a79a34a15f2cbbfab3fc8d152238962c0b3b","tid":1812262,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167e5e0736629ebc473bcbf8863d28d85bd51ccc","tid":1812262,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21f38b9779f1b7b468a582bd9cbeffb32ebb7f5","tid":1812262,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f38588213fa1fbfd9ec8c66082cbbbc5c9a4bb","tid":1812262,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf75dd08010e7947880b010489c0f47430efc2a","tid":1812262,"uid":101034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:15:22.000Z","msg":"和你shop"},{"pid":"867cc2cd916c2f40fa0f179613f1a778413022cf","tid":1812262,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:20:50.000Z","msg":"經濟攬炒 唯一出路"},{"pid":"8670a36daf73f227e5a0393c609690771839b042","tid":1812262,"uid":331861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco